docs.description: Calculate R^2 (coef. of multiple determination); store along with F-test for regression; output 'fift' is written to prefix filename fname

docs.description: Estimate signed maximum of signal; store along with F-test for regression; output 'fift' is written to prefix filename fname

docs.description: Estimate time of signed maximum; store along with F-test for regression; output 'fift' is written to prefix filename fname

docs.title: Maximum percentage change filename prefix
docs.description: Calculate (signed) maximum percentage change of signal from baseline; output 'fift' is written to prefix filename fname

docs.title: Area between signal and baseline filename prefix
docs.description: Calculate area between signal and baseline; store with F-test for regression; output 'fift' is written to prefix filename fname

docs.title: Percentage area of signal filename prefix
docs.description: Percentage area of signal relative to baseline; store with F-test for regression; output 'fift' is written to prefix filename fname

docs.title: Signal parameter estimate filename prefix
docs.description: Estimate kth signal parameter gs[k]; store along with F-test for regression; output 'fift' is written to prefix filename fname

docs.title: Noise parameter estimate filename prefix
docs.description: Estimate kth noise parameter gn[k]; store along with F-test for regression; output 'fift' is written to prefix filename fname

docs.description: Perform t-test for significance of kth noise parameter gn[k]; output 'fitt' is written to prefix filename fname
